=== 1996年被并购 ===
[[File:Odwalla_HQ.JPG|thumb]]
经过五年的业绩增长<ref name="SEC" />，奧德瓦拉于1985年9月正式成立，并于1988年在[[旧金山|旧金山]]扩展销售产品。旧金山风险投资公司H&Q当时是奧德瓦拉的主要投资者之一，向该公司投资了数百万美元。<ref name="music" />到1992年，该公司在加州[[达文波特_(加利福尼亚州)|达文波特]]的总部雇佣了80名员工，销售大约20种不同口味的果汁，每[[品脱|品脱]]售价在1.5美元到2.00美元之间。<ref name="music" /><ref name="prq">{{cite news |url=http://www.mendeley.com/research/purifying-tainted-corporate-image-odwallas-response-e-coli-poisoning-1/ |title=Purifying a tainted corporate image: Odwalla's response to an ''E.coli'' poisoning |last=Thomsen |first=Steven R |author2=Rawson, Bret |year=1998 |work=Public Relations Quarterly |volume=43 |issue=3 |page=35 |access-date=2008-09-08 |dead-url=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120304231608/http://www.mendeley.com/research/purifying-tainted-corporate-image-odwallas-response-e-coli-poisoning-1/ |archive-date=2012-03-04 }}</ref>奧德瓦拉于1993年12月上市（[[纳斯达克|纳斯达克]]股票代码：ODWA），<ref name="hhist" />该公司有35辆送货卡车，近200名员工，每年赚约1300万美元。<ref name="inc29">{{cite web|url=http://www.inc.com/magazine/19930701/3643.html|title=Best Love of Product: True Believers|last=Bianchi|first=Alessandra|date=July 1993|work=Inc. Magazine|access-date=2008-09-06|archive-date=2020-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023094546/https://www.inc.com/magazine/19930701/3643.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>不久之后，奧德瓦拉收购了[[太平洋西北地区|太平洋西北地区]]和[[科罗拉多州|科罗拉多州]]的两家公司，开拓了新的市场。<ref name="hhist" />

为了更好地满足生产需求，奥德瓦拉于1994年在加州[[迪纽巴_(加利福尼亚州)|迪纽巴]]建立了一个新的生产设施。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dinuba.org/labor.html |title=Labor Pool |access-date=2008-08-12 |publisher=City of Dinuba |dead-url=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071006151449/http://www.dinuba.org/labor.html |archive-date=2007-10-06 }}</ref>第二年，公司把总部搬到了加州的半月湾。<ref name="PomaGrand">{{cite press release |title=Odwalla PomaGrand |publisher=Odwalla Inc. |date=2006-03-13 |url=http://www.beverageworld.com/content/view/5454/169 |access-date=2008-08-07 |dead-url=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090203084516/http://www.beverageworld.com/content/view/5454/169 |archive-date=2009-02-03 }}</ref>

这些年的持续增长和外部投资使公司得以扩张和增长：从1994年到1995年，<ref name="prq" />奧德瓦拉的收入增长了两倍，1996年，他们的销售额超过了5900万美元，是有史以来最高的。<ref name="tenq">{{cite press release |title=Quarterly Report Form 10-Q |publisher=Odwalla Inc. |date=1997-11-29 |url=http://www.secinfo.com/dsVSa.718.htm |access-date=2008-08-20 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303205518/http://www.secinfo.com/dsVSa.718.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>这种持续的增长使奧德瓦拉在1996年成为美国最大的鲜果汁公司之一，<ref name="deadly">{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1998/01/04/us/deadly-bacteria-a-new-threat-to-fruit-and-produce-in-us.html|title=Deadly Bacteria a New Threat To Fruit and Produce in U.S.|access-date=2008-08-11|author=[[Christopher_Drew_(reporter)|Christopher Drew]] and [[Pam_Belluck|Pam Belluck]]|date=1988-01-04|work=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]]|quote=Interviews with former Odwalla managers and company documents show that in the weeks before the outbreak, Odwalla began relaxing its standards on accepting blemished fruit and reining in the authority of its own safety officials, culminating in tense, dramatic moments on the morning of Oct. 7, 1996, the day the contaminated juice was pressed. ...|archive-date=2021-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210322135126/https://www.nytimes.com/1998/01/04/us/deadly-bacteria-a-new-threat-to-fruit-and-produce-in-us.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>当时该公司的产品销售到七个州和加拿大部分地区的商店。<ref name="SEC" /><ref name="relations">{{cite news|url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P3-43827623.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150329163924/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P3-43827623.html|dead-url=yes|archive-date=2015-03-29|title=Odwalla|access-date=2008-08-19|author=Evan, Thomas J.|date=1996-07-01|work=[[Public_Relations_Quarterly|Public Relations Quarterly]]}}</ref>据估计，到1999年，他们的销售额将达到1亿美元。这种增长很大程度上是由于人们认为奥德瓦拉的产品比普通果汁更健康，因为它们没有经过[[巴氏消毒|巴氏消毒]]。<ref name="music" /><ref name="deadly" />
=== 逆境、恢复、成长和停止 ===
1996年10月7日，奥德瓦拉用有瑕疵的水果生产了一批苹果汁，导致1人死亡，66名顾客生病。Odwalla为健康果汁市场生产和销售未经高温消毒的果汁。这批货物被大肠杆菌污染了。<ref name="deadly"/>

